{"tid":2211873,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"81磅仍嫌不夠瘦一天磅三次 食物討厭患者做Foodie試食一兩啖 恐懼增磅但鍾意食嘢","createTime":"2020-09-21T11:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:25:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7eee395e94e93036d7f6f96e14f09ecce1710fe7","tid":2211873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBEpooxAidw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmBEpooxAidw&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZokn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=9a162873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBEpooxAidw</a>"},{"pid":"e8ff67247a8edfffa5571b8c1278f3db517ad2cb","tid":2211873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:37:15.000Z","msg":"厭食是「討厭食物」嗎？患上厭食症的琪琪說：「其實很多厭食症患者都很喜歡吃東西，只是即使眼前的東西多好吃，也不能吃，因為內心有個聲音不斷告訴你：『吃下去你就會變胖！』那是一件十分痛苦的事，因為自己已經無法控制自己。」<br />\n<br />\n琪琪在餐廳點了一份迷你漢堡及一杯脫脂奶咖啡，上餐時發現一份漢堡上有兩個迷你漢堡，每一個像奇異果般大。琪琪拿起一個，把另一個塞給攝影師：「你可以幫手吃嗎？我吃不下第二個。」後來她解釋，其實要吃的話，她可以勉強吃下去，但她聽見內心那個制止她的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n其實琪琪以前很喜歡吃東西，一包餃子、兩串燒賣、兩碗飯也吃得完。直至2011年左右，她因感情問題，把自己投入工作，忙起上來便少了吃飯，一天只吃兩餐，漸漸瘦了下來。一瘦下來，便有朋友讚她：「你瘦咗靚咗。」她一上磅，發現自己輕了十多磅。「我的人生似乎一直跟『瘦』扯不上關係，但現在竟瘦了下來，以前穿不下的衣服現在也可以穿了。」"},{"pid":"8ffd6d46d214dc20d67da58328989edab7e26a4e","tid":2211873,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"連登最愛排骨身形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd775500a06c218abcf598c7fcdac3877e2accd","tid":2211873,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ffd6d46d214dc20d67da58328989edab7e26a4e","tid":2211873,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"連登最愛排骨身形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好核突呢種身型<br />\n望到都鳩縮"},{"pid":"36be9b707880ade5ec056caf1f559eea43d5cd1e","tid":2211873,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:45:19.000Z","msg":"好慘其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0195e57cad3aa654cf7440bced229f639b5bd9ef","tid":2211873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4e05eae106c4ebda664924e237b5eec5741f13","tid":2211873,"uid":5994,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"心理問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋眼中重咗0.5磅就好似重咗50磅一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實好想食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完又內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不斷循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abf0fdc8bebb0848c1e76264d7da57be11b48f2","tid":2211873,"uid":317305,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4955cb47c83afe5c327a83bb10b856207e1aed","tid":2211873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df8a9488d957497dfe7b43c2b4278ea2e82ea8e","tid":2211873,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"肥婆不了<br />\n瘦到得骨都不了"},{"pid":"238a929cfe047d6da4e6fa22243dfe7c40d9c7cf","tid":2211873,"uid":327483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"寧可瘦到排骨都不要變成肥婆"}]}